Package org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.querydsl.container

Class QueryContainer

java.lang.Object
org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.querydsl.container.QueryContainer
public class QueryContainer extends Object
Container for various references of the built ES query. Useful to understanding how to interpret and navigate the returned result.

    • columnMask

      public BitSet columnMask​(List<Attribute> columns)
      Since the container contains both the field extractors and the visible columns, compact the information in the listener through a bitset that acts as a mask on what extractors are used for the visible columns.
